headline: Carrier to Host 2025 Investor Day
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR) will host its 2025 Investor Day on May 19, 2025, in New York City. Chairman & CEO David Gitlin and members of the leadership team will discuss the company's strategic priorities.
